          <source>The following example paints the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.Control.Background%2A&gt;</ph> of a button by using an <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush&gt;</ph>.</source>
