        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="109" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>You can control this behavior by setting the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush.Stretch%2A&gt;</ph> property of <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush&gt;</ph> to <ph id="ph3">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch.Uniform&gt;</ph> or <ph id="ph4">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch.UniformToFill&gt;</ph>, which causes the brush to preserve the aspect ratio of the image.</source>
        </trans-unit>
