          <source>If you set the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush.Viewport%2A&gt;</ph> and <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush.TileMode%2A&gt;</ph> properties of an <ph id="ph3">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageBrush&gt;</ph>, you can create a repeating pattern.</source>
